          <h2 class="text-white mb-6 font-black leading-tight" style="font-size: clamp(2.75rem, 5.5vw, 3.75rem);">
            Problemas Comunes que <span style="background: linear-gradient(135deg, #a78bfa 0%, #ec4899 100%); -webkit-background-clip: text; -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;">Reparamos</span>
